<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=10551&amp;p=118872#p118872"><![CDATA[
Technically, most mappers mappers should support 4-screen mapping. The only exception is mapper who already deals with nametable mappring in a standard way : MMC5, and TLSROM/TKSROM (I think it's mapper 118 or something like this).<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38">Bregalad</a> — Wed Oct 02, 2013 1:13 am</p><hr />
